help.item:
raw json syntax: raw json {json call}
The following example will mimic the get user call: +> raw json {"auth":"$auth","method":"user.get","id":2,"params":{"extendoutput":true,"limit":100},"jsonrpc":"2.0"}
note: The automatically updated variable $auth was used. You can choose to use this variable or you can use a different one, however the $auth variable is the one provided by the server upon login.
